@startuml ZMQ RPC Metrics - Full Lifecycle
' Superseded for **code-aligned** lifecycle: see **timing_points_current.puml**.
!pragma teoz true
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam actorBorderColor #666666
skinparam lifelineBorderColor #666666
skinparam lifelineBackgroundColor #F5F5F5

title **ZMQ RPC Metrics - Complete Lifecycle with Threads**

participant "Client Thread" as C <<Client>>
box "Client Module (ZmqStubImpl)" #LightBlue
participant "SimpleGreeting\nAsyncWriteImpl" as AW <<Client>>
participant "SimpleGreeting\nAsyncReadImpl" as AR <<Client>>
end box
participant "MsgQueRef\nSendMsg" as MQ <<MsgQueRef>>
participant "ZmqFrontend\nSendMsg" as FE <<Frontend>>
participant "MsgQueMgr\nPrefetcher Thread" as PM <<Prefetcher>>
database "Network" as Net
participant "ZmqService" as S <<Server>>
participant "Worker Thread\nPool" as W <<Worker>>
participant "Business Handler\n(impl_->CallMethod)" as H <<Handler>>
participant "ZmqService\nBackendToFrontend" as B2F <<Backend>>
participant "ZmqServerImpl\nServiceToClient" as SImpl <<ServerImpl>>

note across
  **Client Ticks** (zmq_constants.h)
  - CLIENT_ENQUEUE: 消息放入 outBound queue (zmq_stub_impl.h L163)
  - CLIENT_STUB_SEND: SendMsg 返回后 (zmq_stub_impl.h L172)
  - CLIENT_DEQUEUE: prefetcher 从队列取出 (zmq_msg_queue.h L682)
  - CLIENT_ZMQ_SEND: ❌ MISSING
  - CLIENT_RECV: 收到回复 (zmq_stub_impl.h L232)

  **Server Ticks**
  - SERVER_RECV: zmq_msg_recv 返回后 (zmq_service.cpp L1189)
  - SERVER_DEQUEUE: 从 worker 队列取出 (zmq_service.cpp L722)
  - SERVER_EXEC_END: 业务 handler 完成 (zmq_service.cpp L729)
  - SERVER_ZMQ_SEND: zmq_msg_send 成功后 (zmq_server_impl.cpp L187)
end note

== **Client: 发送请求 (AsyncWriteImpl)** ==

C -> AW : SimpleGreetingAsyncWrite(req)
activate C
activate AW
note over AW: 1. 创建 MetaPb + frames

AW -> AW : RecordTick(meta, CLIENT_ENQUEUE)
note over AW: **CLIENT_ENQUEUE** ✓

AW -> MQ : mQue->SendMsg(p)
note over MQ: 2. **p = (meta, frames)**\nmsgQue_->Send(ele)

MQ -> FE : msgQue_->Send()
activate FE
note over FE: 3. ZmqFrontend::SendMsg\n创建 ConnMsgFrames

FE -> PM : msgQue_->Send() → 队列
deactivate FE

note over PM: 4. 消息进入 MsgQueMgr 队列

deactivate AW

== **Prefetcher Thread: 异步发送** ==

activate PM
PM -> PM : PrefetchMsg 取消息

note over PM: 5. **CLIENT_DEQUEUE** ✓\nprefetcher 从队列取出

PM -> PM : routeFn_ → SendDirect
note over PM: 6. zmq_msg_send()\n⚠️ **CLIENT_ZMQ_SEND MISSING**

deactivate PM

== **Network** ==

Net -> S : TCP/UDS
activate S

== **Server: 接收 & 分发** ==

note over S: 7. **SERVER_RECV** ✓\nzmq_msg_recv 返回后

S -> S : RouteToRegBackend

note over S: 8. 分发到 worker\n(numRegularSockets_)

== **Worker Thread: 处理请求** ==

S -> W : workerCBs_[id]->WorkerEntry()
activate W

note over W: 9. **SERVER_DEQUEUE** ✓\nworker_->ReceiveMsg(inMsg)\n从 worker 队列取出

W -> H : impl_->CallMethod(worker_, meta, ...)
activate H

note over H: 10. 业务逻辑执行\n(e.g., SimpleGreeting)

deactivate H
note over W: 11. **SERVER_EXEC_END** ✓\nRecordTick(meta, TICK_SERVER_EXEC_END)

W -> B2F : replyQueue_->Put(reply)
note over W: 12. 放入 replyQueue

deactivate W

== **BackendToFrontend: 回包** ==

activate B2F
B2F -> SImpl : ServiceToClient(p)
activate SImpl

note over SImpl: 13. **SERVER_ZMQ_SEND** ✓\nRecordTick(meta, TICK_SERVER_ZMQ_SEND)\nRecordServerLatencyMetrics(meta)\nPushFrontProtobufToFrames(meta, frames)

SImpl -> SImpl : frontend_->SendAllFrames(frames)

deactivate SImpl
deactivate B2F

== **Network** ==

Net -> AR : TCP/UDS
activate AR

== **Client: 接收回复 (AsyncReadImpl)** ==

C -> AR : SimpleGreetingAsyncRead(tagId, rsp)
note over AR: 14. **CLIENT_RECV** ✓\nmQue->ReceiveMsg(rsp)\nRecordTick(rsp.first, TICK_CLIENT_RECV)

AR -> AR : GetClientMeta()
note over AR: 15. 获取 clientMeta\n(ENQUEUE, STUB_SEND, DEQUEUE)

AR -> AR : Merge ticks
note over AR: 16. 合并到 rsp.first\nRecordRpcLatencyMetrics(rsp.first)

deactivate AR
deactivate C

== **Metrics 计算** ==

note across
  **Client:**
  - CLIENT_QUEUING = ZMQ_SEND - ENQUEUE ❌ **MISSING**
  - CLIENT_STUB_SEND = DEQUEUE - STUB_SEND ✓

  **Server:**
  - SERVER_QUEUE_WAIT = DEQUEUE - RECV ✓
  - SERVER_EXEC = EXEC_END - DEQUEUE ✓
  - SERVER_REPLY = ZMQ_SEND - EXEC_END ✓

  **E2E:**
  - E2E = RECV - ENQUEUE ✓
  - NETWORK = E2E - SERVER_EXEC ✓
end note

== **关键问题** ==

note across
  **Issue #1: CLIENT_ZMQ_SEND MISSING**
  - 原因: SendDirect 在 prefetcher 线程
  - clientMeta 在 AsyncWriteImpl 线程已固定
  - callback 无法传递到 clientMeta

  **Issue #2: MetaPb 拷贝**
  - meta → p.first (copy) → clientMeta (copy)
  - 应使用 const 引用传递避免拷贝

  **Issue #3: SERVER_SEND vs ZMQ_SEND**
  - TICK_SERVER_SEND 仍在多处记录
  - 应统一使用 TICK_SERVER_ZMQ_SEND
end note

@enduml
